about.summary: Fast, versatile and user-friendly landscape evolution models

name: fastscape
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "fastscape" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0alpha" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/fastscape-lem/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 16610db6bfcee82f312c813c093bdc0a96846c109935c367d3ee9d0498fa0b86

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3
    - xarray-simlab >=0.3.0
    - fastscapelib-f2py >=2.8.1
    - numba

test:
  imports:
    - fastscape

about:
  home: https://github.com/fastscape-lem/fastscape
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Fast, versatile and user-friendly landscape evolution models'
  doc_url: https://fastscape.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/fastscape-lem/fastscape

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - benbovy
